No. 1/34/1/2004-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 15th January, 2004
25 Pausa, 1925(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 15th January,
2004 :-
Shri N.T. Shanmugam relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Food Processing
Industries;
i)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Food Processing Industries; and
ii)
Shri A.K. Moorthy relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Railways.
i)
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
